item.title: Prayer bpn10250 in Māori
item.description: He Pouwetewete i te raruraru i tua atu i Te Atua? Meatia: Korōria ki Te Atua! Ko Ia Te Atua. Ko ngā mea katoa Āna pononga, katoa he whakarongo ki Tāna e hiahia ai! (Source category: MŌ TE WHAKAPĀTARITARI ME TE RARURARU) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 10250)

item.title: Prayer bpn10251 in Māori
item.description: Ko tāku tono ki a Koe ki Tōu kaha, e tōku Atua! Kia kaua ahau e whara i ngā wā whakawā, ā i ngā wā kore whakarongo kia ārahina tika aku tapuwae e Tōu hiringa. Ko Koe Te Atua, whaikaha ana ki Tāu e hiahia ai. Kāore e taea e tētahi te karo i Tāu e Hiahia ai, i Tāu e Whai ai. (Source category: MŌ TE WHAKAPĀTARITARI ME TE RARURARU) (Bahaiprayers.
